sentences: By 2000 he had moved to Montreal.
That year, under the stage name Frankie Sparo, he released his first album, My Red Scare, accompanying his slow songs and gruff voice with guitar.
He continued to perform in Montreal, and a second album, Arena Hostile, was released in 2001.
The album was released in 2003, and appeared on the !
